titleStmt.title: Bare Demo of IEEEtran.cls for Conferences

div.head: Introduction
div.p: This demo file is intended to serve as a starter file for IEEE conference papers produced under LaTeX using IEEEtran.cls version 1.8 and later. I wish you the best of success.
